snippet.title: Deewaane (Selfiee) - Akshay K | Jacqueline F | Emraan H | Aditya Y | Stebin B | Tanishk B | Kunaal V
snippet.description:
Star Studios presents in association with Dharma Productions, Prithviraj Productions, Magic Frames & Cape Of Good Films.
A Dharma Productions Film SELFIEE
Starring Akshay Kumar, Emraan Hashmi, Nushrratt Bharuccha, Diana Penty
Directed by Raj Mehta
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Aruna Bhatia, Supriya Menon, Karan Johar, Prithviraj Sukumaran, Apoorva Mehta & Listin Stephen
Screenplay and Dialogues by Rishhabh Sharrma
Music Supervised by Azeem Dayani
All Streaming Links Hereüëâ https://ingrooves.lnk.to/Deewaane

Create Reels hereüëâ https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/540290264619243/

Song : Deewaane 
Singer : Aditya Yadav, Stebin Ben, Altamash Faridi
Original Composer : Aditya Yadav
Recreated by : Tanishk Bagchi
Programmed and arranged by : Tanishk Bagchi
New Lyrics : Kunaal Vermaa 
Original Lyrics : Aditya Yadav
Video Director : Agam Mann & Azeem Mann
DOP : Shinda Singh
Choreographer : Adil Shaikh
Strings : Mert Kemanci
Chorus Boys : Sudhanshu Shome, Rakesh Deol, Udayveer Singh, Arjun Pandey, Rehan Khan
Guitar : Somu Seal
Mandolin : Tapas Roy
Mix and Master: Eric Pillai @ (Future Sound of Bombay)
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani
Associate Music Supervisor: Megha Vikaas Bali
Special Thanks: Sumeet Kr Tyagi

Special Thanks: Ingrooves Team https://www.ingrooves.com/ 

Play Desi Music Factory 
Founder & CEO - Anshul Garg 
PlayDMF Project Head - Raghav Sharma 
Label Manager - Gaurav Bharti  
PlayDMF team - Gaurav Arora , Asheema Chauhan & Sankalp Garg 
Special thanks - Rajat Nagpal
Digital Promotions - Underdog Digital 
YouTube Promotions - Net Media

Lyrics

Mazaa aa jaata hai
Adhoori baaton se
Koi mann jaata hai
Zaroori yaaron se
Jo dekhi na suni aisi
Hume duniya dikhati hai
Deewaane hum nahin hote
Deewaani raat aati hai 
Hume unki uhne meri
Mohabbat yaad aati hai

Nazar aati hain zulfon mein
Ghataein badalon jaisi
Yeh dil karne laga unse
Wafaein paglon jaisi
Usse jab dekhte hain toh
Badal jaata hai yeh lehza
Zubaan pe aa hi jaati hai
Adayein shayaron jaisi
Unhe jab yaad karte hain
Tabhi barsaat aati hai
Deewaane hum nahin hote
Deewaani raat aati hai 
Hume unki uhne meri
Mohabbat yaad aati hai

Nahin koi gila humein
Jo na iss baar maanenge
Abhi chahe mana kar de
Kabhi toh yaar maanenge
Miley jo cheez aasani se 
Toh usme mazaa kaisa
Unhe mera banana tak
Na hum bhi haar maanenge
Suna hai chahatein sachi
Nahin barbaad jaati hain
Deewaane hum nahin hote
Deewaani raat aati hai 
Hume unki uhne meri
Mohabbat yaad aati hai

#akshaykumar #emraanhashmi #jacquelinefernandez

snippet.title: My Team Left Me Alone....üò≠ MR. INDIAN HACKER
snippet.description:
my team left me alone and went on a mission of exploring India. 5 teams, 5 places & 10 people. They went to different cities like Goa, Meghalaya, Kufri, Kerala & Rameshwaram. 
.
.
Part-1 Link - https://youtu.be/_dZgvOByRe4
.
.
Watch Their Individual Vlogs Here :- https://youtube.com/@teammihofficial
.
.
They all made a vlog so you guys (our Titanium Army) can also enjoy and see the beauty of our beloved country. Therefore , let us present to you the biggest project we ever made with a lot of hard work and days of editing. #India #MrIndianHacker #Vlog.
.
.
Song Credits To The Respected Artists :-

Song: Bahane Bana Kar
Singer: Avinash Baghel (BCS)
Lyrics: Avinash Baghel (BCS)
Composer: Agnivesh Baghel (Ragasur)
Mixing & Mastering: Agnivesh Baghel (Ragasur)

Song: Ishaq Hua Hai Mujhe
Singer: Avinash Baghel (BCS)
Lyrics: Hemant Gairola (BCS)
Composer: Agnivesh Baghel (Ragasur)
Mixing & Mastering: Agnivesh Baghel (Ragasur)
.
.
Comment down your favourite part from this vlog & let us know If you want us to continue this series, if yes then which places should we add next. 

Jai Hind Jai Bharat

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3710 - 4 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3710: Jethalal Ka Promise
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha scares himself by daydreaming about going bald in Gokuldham. He imagines everyone laughing at him while Babita refuses to help. As he wakes up from his imagination, he sees Nattu and Bagha who have bought "jalebi fafda" for him. Jetha refuses to eat it and decides to run away. He is stopped by Babita and Iyer at the door and comes back inside the shop to tell them the truth. Iyer is angry while Babita is left shocked as Jethalal tries to tell the whole story. Watch the episode to know more.
 
Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3710, 4 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

 ‚Ä¢ ‡§π‡§∞‡§≠‡§∞‡§æ ‡§°‡§æ‡§≥ 2 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Bengal Gram 2 Cup

‡§ï‡§£‡§ø‡§ï ‡§Æ‡§≥‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä | For making dough 
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ó‡§µ‡•ç‡§π‡§æ‡§ö‡•á ‡§™‡•Ä‡§† 4 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Wheat flour 4 cups
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§Æ‡•Ä‡§† ¬Ω tsp | Salt to taste
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§§‡•á‡§≤ 2-3 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡•á | oil 2-3 tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä ‡§ó‡§∞‡§ú‡•á‡§®‡•Å‡§∏‡§æ‡§∞ | Water as required

Method ‚Äì
 ‚Ä¢ For making dough in a wheat flour add salt and knead the dough, rest for 20 mins and then apply some oil and knead soft dough again.
 ‚Ä¢ Wash and soak chana daal for about 30 minutes. 
 ‚Ä¢ Heat up water in a pressure cooker, add soaked daal along with water, add turmeric and oil and take 4-5 whistles on med heat.
 ‚Ä¢ Once cooked, separate daal and water. 
 ‚Ä¢ Once daal is at room temp, grind into mixer grinder.
 ‚Ä¢ Now add ground daal into a kadhai, add chopped jaggery and turn on the gas flame.
 ‚Ä¢ Now saute till mixture gets thickness then add cardamom and nutmeg powder.
 ‚Ä¢ Then turn off the heat and let the puran cool down completely. 
 ‚Ä¢ Now take ball size dough, dust some rice flour and fill the equal amount of puran and roll roti / puranpoli . dust rice flour whenever required,
 ‚Ä¢ Roast the puranpoli, apply ghee or oil.

Puranpoli | ‡§™‡•Å‡§∞‡§£‡§™‡•ã‡§≥‡•Ä ‚Äì 
‡§™‡•Å‡§∞‡§£ ‡§¨‡§®‡§µ‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä | For making Puran
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§π‡§∞‡§≠‡§∞‡§æ ‡§°‡§æ‡§≥ 2 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Bengal Gram 2 Cup
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§π‡§≥‡§¶ ¬º tsp | Turmeric ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§§‡•á‡§≤ 2 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡•á | Oil 2 tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä | Water 
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ó‡•Ç‡§≥ 2 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Jaggery 2 Cup
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§µ‡•á‡§≤‡§ö‡•Ä ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ¬º tsp | Cardamom pw ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ú‡§æ‡§Ø‡§´‡§≥ ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ¬º tsp | Nutmeg pw ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§∏‡•Å‡§Ç‡§† ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ‡•ß/‡•™ tsp | Ginger pw 1/4 tsp
‡§ï‡§£‡§ø‡§ï ‡§Æ‡§≥‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä | For making dough 
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ó‡§µ‡•ç‡§π‡§æ‡§ö‡•á ‡§™‡•Ä‡§† 4 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Wheat flour 4 cups
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§Æ‡•Ä‡§† ¬Ω tsp | Salt to taste
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§§‡•á‡§≤ 2-3 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡•á | oil 2-3 tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä ‡§ó‡§∞‡§ú‡•á‡§®‡•Å‡§∏‡§æ‡§∞ | Water as required

Method ‚Äì
 ‚Ä¢ For making dough in a wheat flour add salt and knead the dough, rest for 20 mins and then apply some oil and knead soft dough again.
 ‚Ä¢ Wash and soak chana daal for about 30 minutes. 
 ‚Ä¢ Heat up water in a pressure cooker, add soaked daal along with water, add turmeric and oil and take 4-5 whistles on med heat.
 ‚Ä¢ Once cooked, separate daal and water. 
 ‚Ä¢ Once daal is at room temp, grind into mixer grinder.
 ‚Ä¢ Now add ground daal into a kadhai, add chopped jaggery and turn on the gas flame.
 ‚Ä¢ Now saute till mixture gets thickness then add cardamom and nutmeg powder.
 ‚Ä¢ Then turn off the heat and let the puran cool down completely. 
 ‚Ä¢ Now take ball size dough, dust some rice flour and fill the equal amount of puran and roll roti / puranpoli . dust rice flour whenever required,
 ‚Ä¢ Roast the puranpoli, apply ghee or oil.

snippet.title: Every Indian During Holi | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys , 
This Holi Video has every Holi situation we experience. How Indians celebrate holi . The crazy masti of Holi . Revenge wali holi , pyaar wali holi , dosto ke sath , holi fest ki holi , college wali holi , holi pool party , exams wali holi . During board exams skipping holi festival and studying whole day , Indian mom scoulding and letting go out tom play holi with friends on streets with water ballons , pichkari , herbal colors and forcing to go to tuition on Holi , deciding holi songs playlist , grooving on ap dhillon songs , enjoying bhang thandai , beer , gol gappe , dahi bhalle , gujia sweets , getting gifts from relatives gulal , rang , all the colors , pichkari , desi ghee gujia , hugging enemies sorting out the grudges , hitting with water balloons , water guns , dancing , enjoying holika dhayan , the festival of colors . Girls planning to go parlour after holi so that holi colours comes out with waxing , facial , eyebrow threading , while girl got her periods and is avoiding holi cause she can't deal with tampons , menstrual cups and pads . After marraige first holi , lakde wale in lakdi walo ke ghar , making dahi bhalle , dancing , colouring the newlyweds , new couple having their romantic holi in front of in laws , mother in law and father in law , devar , devrani , jethani , nanad all in Mom house . Planning to go out to celebrate holi with big group travelling in train bus to vrindavan , brij ki holi , jaipur , udaipur holi , mathura holi foreigners wali Holi . Society ki holi party with all the food stalls , rang , gujia , gol gappe , sweets , pickari , chandhan , bhang , kulfi . Ladies dressing like Hema malini , Rekha white suit , bandni duppata , doing holi fashion in indian traditional wear , buying Ready made gobar uple . Packing holi Gifts for Indian relatives , kids buying water guns every holi , asking more colours , discussing kodda holi of haryana . School friends deciding to play after school in school corridoor , Hiding colour packets in school bag to play holi with school friends , ruining school uniform with colours , mummy scoulding  . Chintu Chinki Bhai Behen after holi in stained holi colours Mom savitri feeding cold puri , thandi puri achar , sabzi , and tea , after bathing multiple times to get the color out , Indian family getting to bed to sleep , plans to eat faluda kulfiin the evening enjoying with a good movie . Brother going out with his bro friends again playing holi with grease . Sister telling Mom , and mom daughter freaking out  . Taking out revenge by applying colours, the foodies, getting painted first by the bf/gf, mixing pakka color into herbal colors, balloon horror created in society that we go through in holi days, and The Best Holi Fight between two groups.. Well you will love it and Relate with this video.. Enjoy and laugh out loud. 
Do Share it with everyone, Comment your fav part and like krdena Video guys.. Subscribe the Channel for more amazing videos . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family  .. Comment down your Fav Part, 
Like, Share and

Prithviraj Chauhan vs Muhammad Ghori | Battle of Tarain | By Prashant Dhawan

Prithviraja III, popularly known as Prithviraj Chauhan or Rai Pithora was a king from the Chahamana (Chauhan) dynasty. He ruled Sapadalaksha, the traditional Chahamana territory, in present-day north-western India. He controlled much of the present-day Rajasthan, Haryana, and Delhi; and some parts of Punjab, Madhya Pradesh and Uttar Pradesh. His capital was located at Ajayameru (modern Ajmer).

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 21 Teaser - 2nd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 21 Teaser - 2nd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Yumna Zaidi as Meerab

Bushra Ansari as Salma

snippet.title: Pakistan Economic Crisis - Pakistan's internal problem with Taliban | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
Get our Red Following Love T shirt here: https://bit.ly/3C7SGeL

In this video, Abhi and Niyu discuss how Pakistan's focus on militarization of bordering areas contributed towards the current Pakistani Economic Crisis. 

Welcome to our latest video exploring the complex and often turbulent relationship between Pakistan and Afghanistan. As neighboring countries that share a long and porous border, Pakistan and Afghanistan have a deeply intertwined history that has been marked by conflict, cooperation, and occasional periods of stability.

In this video, we delve into the key issues that have shaped the relationship between these two countries, from the Soviet invasion of Afghanistan in the 1980s to the rise of the Taliban in the 1990s and the US-led invasion of Afghanistan in 2001. We also explore the role of regional and international actors in shaping the dynamic between Pakistan and Afghanistan, including India, Iran, China, and the United States.

Our video features interviews with experts and analysts who provide insights into the complex geopolitical and security challenges facing both countries. We also examine the economic and cultural ties between Pakistan and Afghanistan, as well as the ongoing efforts to promote peace and stability in the region.

Whether you're a student of international relations, a history buff, or simply curious about the complex relationship between Pakistan and Afghanistan, our video is a must-watch. So sit back, grab some popcorn, and join us for a deep dive into the history, politics, and culture of these two fascinating countries.

#pakistaneconomy #geopolitics #abhiandniyu

snippet.description:
In a haunted house shadows of evil spirits are noticed by pedestrians. Sumer, Mugdha and Gini are attacked by an evil shadow. The next morning Mugdha gets to know that her brother Balvinder has got a job of a music teacher in the same haunted house. Since then Balvinder has gone missing and a blood-stained Tiffin box has reached his house. How will CID solve this case? Is the bungalow really haunted? Watch this episode to find out.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
‚Ä¢ Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
‚Ä¢ Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
‚Ä¢ Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
‚Ä¢ Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
‚Ä¢ Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
‚Ä¢ Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
‚Ä¢ Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
‚Ä¢ Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1344
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #livcrime #‡§∏‡•Ä‡§Ü‡§à‡§°‡•Ä #NewCID #LatestCID

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: AGEING PARENTS | Stand up Comedy by Abijit Ganguly
snippet.description:
Desi parents are good at lot of things. One thing they are definitely not is looking after their own health. Stand-up bit from my experience of dealing with my now ageing parents. This bit is fairly close to my heart, hope you like it.
If you are an ageing parent and watching this, just one request, be mindful of your own health as you age, that's the best gift/lesson you can give to your kids.

Performing some shows around. Ticket links to the shows in the link below.

Show links: https://linktr.ee/AbijitGanguly

For show queries, contact on +91 89286 08556 or drop a mail at abijitganguly@gmail.com.

snippet.title: Life Update...it's been tough üíî
snippet.description:
Hey guys

Just felt like sitting down and catching you up on life. I know a lot of you are going through so much yourself, and I want you to know that you are not alone.
We're all trying to find our light and we will, someday...

I love you
Xx

I see your support and it means so much to be and baby.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3709 - 3 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3709: Jethalal Ke Baal Khatre Mein Hai
--------------------------------------------------------
Nattu Kaka and Jetha try desperately to set up the 85-inch Ramson TV for Ronita, Babita Ji's relative, but are unsuccessful. Jetha becomes anxious as Iyer, Babita, and Ronita approach Gada Electronics. For any last-minute advice on how to get out of the predicament, he calls Taarak. Bagha urges Bawri not to call during business hours since he feels awful for his boss. Bawri is also instructed by Bagha to cease returning to Gada Electronics so frequently. Finally, Ronita shows up at the store and gives Jetha a bouquet of flowers for setting up the unique model of this TV. What will occur next? Will Jetha be required to lose his hair? Remain tuned!
 
Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3709, 3 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000211949

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #SAB

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop. 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

Click here to watch the episode of TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Tere Bin Episode 20 Teaser - 1st March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
